extendedInfo.description: Listen to the timeless love songs from your favorite Disney movies like Beauty and the Beast, Aladdin, Lion King and many more...  Follow the lyrics and sing along!Songs include: -A Dream Is A Wish Your Heart Makes-A Whole New World-As Long As There's Christmas-Bare Necessities-Be Our Guest-Beauty and the Beast (Tale as Old as Time)-Belle-Can You Feel The Love Tonight?-Circle of Life-Colours of the Wind-Everybody Wants To Be A Cat-Friend Like Me-Go The Distance-Hakuna Matata-He Lives in You-Heigh Ho-He's A Tramp-I Just Can't Wait to be King-I Won't Say I'm In Love-I'll Make A Man Out Of You-I'm Wishing/One Song-Kiss the Girl-Once Upon A Dream-One Jump-Oo-de-lally-Part of Your World-Reflection-Rescue Aid Society-Sing Sweet Nightingale-So This Is Love-Something There-Son of Man-The Best of Friends-Under the Sea-Why Should I Worry?-You Can Fly-Zero to Hero-many more...This application is brought to you totally free with the help of search monetization. I have opted to use this to be able to keep creating more free apps for you. Please note that with this app you will receive a few search points on your device, all are easily deleted or replaced. Thank you for your understanding.
